
mode.vim - TDD mode control script for vim

# Key-bind
<leader>mt     : mode think
<leader>mr     : mode red
<leader>mg     : mode green
<leader>mf     : mode refactor
<leader>m<C-m> : rotate mode (think -> red -> green -> refactor)

# Settings
s:color_bar
  0 : use short color bar
  1 : use logn color bar
mode name
  s:mode_think
  s:mode_red
  s:mode_green
  s:mode_refactor

# Known bugs
Can't control tow or more mode at same time, because share User1 highlight group and my_mode variable.
